    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1961-08-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1961-08-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="390"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d390">
                <head>390. Note from Pezzullo to May, August 21<note n="1" type="source"
                        xml:id="d390fn1">No reply necessary to correspondence from Secretary
                            <persName corresp="#p_FOL_1">Freeman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            corresp="#p_BCB_1">Bowles</persName>. No subject mentioned. No
                        classification marking. 1 p. Washington National Records Center, <gloss
                            target="#t_RG_1">RG</gloss> 286, <gloss target="#t_AID_1">AID</gloss>
                        Administrator Files: <gloss target="#t_FRC_1">FRC</gloss> 65 A 481,
                        Agriculture, <gloss target="#t_FY_1">FY</gloss> 1962.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1961-08-21">August 21, 1961</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d390-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d390-1"/>
                <p rend="sectiontitleital">Draft Reply by Under Secretary to Letter from Sec.
                        <persName corresp="#p_FOL_1">Freeman</persName>
                </p>
                <p>U has gone over the history of this correspondence, and does not believe any
                    further reply to <persName corresp="#p_FOL_1">Freeman</persName> is required at
                    this time. Mr. <persName corresp="#p_BCB_1">Bowles</persName> and Mr. <persName
                        corresp="#p_FOL_1">Freeman</persName> have seen each other several times
                    since the letter was written, and the reply as drafted is overtaken by
                    events.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>Lawrence Pezzullo</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
